{"language": "javascript", "mode": "NEP", "expected_edit_kind": "Jump", "label": "JS NEP: add export propagates to import statement far away", "file_path": "module.js", "cursor_line": 6, "original_content": "// Module for utilities\n\nconst utils = {};\n\nutils.format = (s) => s.trim();\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\n\nmodule.exports = utils;", "current_content": "// Module for utilities\n\nconst utils = {};\n\nutils.format = (s) => s.trim();\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\nutils.validate = (s) => s.length > 0;\n\nmodule.exports = utils;", "prompt": "<|file_sep|>module.js.diff\noriginal:\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\n\nmodule.exports = utils;\nupdated:\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\nutils.validate = (s) => s.length > 0;\n\nmodule.exports = utils;\n<|file_sep|>original/module.js\n// Module for utilities\n\nconst utils = {};\n\nutils.format = (s) => s.trim();\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\n\nmodule.exports = utils;\n<|file_sep|>current/module.js\n// Module for utilities\n\nconst utils = {};\n\nutils.format = (s) => s.trim();\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\nutils.validate = (s) => s.length > 0;\n\nmodule.exports = utils;\n<|file_sep|>updated/module.js", "response": "\n// Module for utilities\n\nconst utils = {};\n\nutils.format = (s) => s.trim();\nutils.parse = (s) => JSON.parse(s);\nutils.validate = (s) => s.length > 0;\n\nmodule.exports = utils;\n", "error": null, "elapsed_seconds": 0.326}
