{"language": "rust", "mode": "FIM", "expected_edit_kind": "Inline", "label": "Rust FIM: complete impl block method", "file_path": "rect.rs", "cursor_line": 7, "original_content": "", "current_content": "struct Rect {\n    width: f64,\n    height: f64,\n}\n\nimpl Rect {\n    fn area(&self) -> f64 {\n\n    }\n\n    fn perimeter(&self) -> f64 {\n        2.0 * (self.width + self.height)\n    }\n}", "prompt": "<|file_sep|>original/rect.rs\n\n<|file_sep|>current/rect.rs\nstruct Rect {\n    width: f64,\n    height: f64,\n}\n\nimpl Rect {\n    fn area(&self) -> f64 {\n\n    }\n\n    fn perimeter(&self) -> f64 {\n        2.0 * (self.width + self.height)\n    }\n}\n<|file_sep|>updated/rect.rs", "response": "\nstruct Rect {\n    width: f64,\n    height: f64,\n}\n\nimpl Rect {\n    fn area(&self) -> f64 {\n        self.width * self.height\n    }\n\n    fn perimeter(&self) -> f64 {\n        2.0 * (self.width + self.height)\n    }\n}\n", "error": null, "elapsed_seconds": 0.51}
